In the fictional '''[[Archie Comics|Archie]]''' Universe, '''Archie's Gang''' refers to the collection of people consisting of [[Archie Andrews (comics)|Archie Andrews]], [[Betty Cooper]], [[Jughead Jones]], [[Veronica Lodge]], [[Dilton Doiley]] and [[Reggie Mantle]].

Honorary members of the gang include
[[Hot Dog (Archie)|Hot Dog]]

The gang frequently hangs out at [[Pop Tate]]'s establishment, performs before live audiences as [[The Archies]], perform various school club duties at [[Riverdale High School (Archie Comics)|Riverdale High School]], and spend vacation time together.

